platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.ta.k: やりごたえ抜群サバイバルゲーム

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: And just when we were getting the hang of surviving the wilderness, too… Now we’re crafting boats, exploring tropical islands, and battling through the night. Klei and CAPY are a match made in heaven, and we can’t believe we get to witness their Burton-esque nightmare.

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.sh.k: Learn to survive in this world of both wonders and hidden dangers.
你能以科學家頭腦，善用資源，在滿佈奇珍異獸的荒野中求生嗎？
受困荒島，你得善用資源求生，島上生物、炎熱天氣都是需克服的挑戰。
